Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:50.17,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}非常事態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:52.20,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Rising noise, I want to prove
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.13,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}押し潰されそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:57.88,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}理想がせめぎあう攻防戦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.77,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}吠えてみたくて　騒めき始める
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:05.63,IN1-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}はね返る心臓　響く合図<チャイム>
