Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.99,0:20:20.92,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}全部咬碎吞下
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.92,0:20:25.16,IN1-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}吃飽了  多謝款待
